Hello vv, it's great to meet you. My name is Alex, and I'll be conducting this technical interview for a Python and Flask developer position. I'll be asking you a series of questions to assess your technical skills and experience.

Before we begin, I want to assure you that this is a relaxed and conversational interview. Feel free to ask for clarification or take your time to respond to any question. We'll be covering a range of topics, from Python basics to Flask and web development.
